    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7 and cut your<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>wedges</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>half</strong> your<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp \u2013 these are your <strong>paprika wedges</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the wedges are cooking, chop your<strong> cod fillet[s]</strong> lengthways<strong> </strong>into finger-width strips</p><p>Pat dry with kitchen paper \u2013 these are your <strong>cod goujons</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>to a large bowl with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and mix it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>spiced cornflour</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cod goujons </strong>to the <strong>spiced cornflour</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the cod goujons are fully coated, then set aside \u2013 these are your <strong>coated cod goujons</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then finely slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>to a large bowl with<strong> </strong>your <strong>mayo </strong>and the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and mix it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>creamy slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>When the wedges are almost ready, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>(enough to cover the base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated cod goujons </strong>and cook for 5 min on each side or until crisp and cooked through \u2013 these are your <strong>southern fried cod goujons</strong></p><p>Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in batches!</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-fried-cod-goujons-paprika-wedges-and-slaw/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>southern fried cod goujons </strong>with the <strong>paprika wedges</strong>, <strong>creamy slaw</strong> and a dollop of your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>ketchup </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
